p dawg
I agree with the author, but the true hell is that standing up in the manner suggested can have consequences for your family, too. If we were all single with no kids, we could stand up and fight this crap. But when you have a family, losing your job, even if it's for fighting the good fight, puts that family at risk. I don't know what the solution is, but that's an aspect of the problem that wasn't addressed in the article.
